pr_body:
WIP pull request for artboard framework
CheckList
- [x] Artboard Component to manage multiple canvas layers
- underlay layer
- interaction layer.
- [x] Underlay layer canvas for View with a ViewModel.
- [x] Canvas manager component for handling multiple canvases.
- [x] Methods for zoom-level, background, etc in view of (canvas manager).
- [ ] Add Model for each canvas with actions including drawing, centering, cleaning, etc.
- [ ] Intercation layer to position the sprites and signals other canvas component.

Issue: #58
